[46;30;1m 3. --skip-ownership [0m

[2m  Skips CODEOWNERS entirely: no file fetch, no ownership lookup.[0m
[2m  The measurement is just Size × Risk, so the output ends on the[0m
[2m  Base CRU line with NO ownership table (distinct from the genuine[0m
[2m  no-CODEOWNERS case in section 2, which still shows a ~ Unowned[0m
[2m  row). Resolving your identity is implied-off too.[0m

