[46;30;1m 5. Insufficient token access (graceful degradation) [0m

[2m  When the token can't read your team memberships (the Codespaces[0m
[2m  default GITHUB_TOKEN, or a fine-grained PAT without read:org),[0m
[2m  gh-cru can't tell which team-owned lines are yours. It does NOT[0m
[2m  fail; it measures what it can and footnotes the gap. The footnote[0m
[2m  fires only when your stake would read 0 AND you're not already a[0m
[2m  direct @login owner, i.e. exactly when the 0 might mislead.[0m

